content: Hello ! :wave: I'm from France, developing for a living for 5 years and I'm constantly trying to learnnew things, I'm into web development (PHP, JS/TS) but not really into lower level stuff, I think learning and practising some Rust could make me a better developer ! I'm currently doing the rustling course, is there ant place I can ask my noob's question ?

The Discord server is preferred for general questions. Zulip is mostly used by compiler, library and tool developers, and you'll probably get faster answers on Discord. But you can ask here anyway, and some people do.
